        <item>
            <title>Version 1.1.0</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2025 15:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>4</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
            
            ### Added
            - Visual indicator (orange dot) for worktrees with uncommitted changes
            - Preference option to bypass deletion confirmation dialogs
            - Force deletion of worktrees with uncommitted changes using `--force` flag
            
            ### Changed
            - Improved deletion warning dialog to explicitly mention loss of uncommitted changes, untracked files, and stashed work
            - Optimized dirty status checking to run asynchronously in the background
            - Added throttling to prevent excessive status checks (limited to once every 5 seconds)
            
            ### Fixed
            - Loading screen appearing too frequently when checking worktree status
            - Performance improvement by removing synchronous dirty checking during initial load
            
            ]]></description>
